Summary: black triangular aircraft with with and yellow lights, about 6 or more exterior lights
divs: sighting detailsit is 3\6\2013 11:51pm and about 20 minutes ago while jogging in paradise hills neighborhood in san diego i saw a black triangular aircraft. there were exterior lights on so there was no effort at discretion. i saw it coming from the southeast moving in a northwest direction. it was hovering momentarily, then slowly moving toward the naval base i think. i was able to view it for approximately 5 minutes. it was making a loud rumbling sound and was above the tree line but lower than a commercial aircraft would fly. i worked in the airline industry for 16 years, and lived near an airport and this was definitely not like any commercial aircraft or helicopter i have seen. perhaps it was a military aircraft. whatever it was, it looked really cool and i have never seen anything like that before. i am shocked how slowly it moved and still amazed at the number lights and it's shape. very interesting!
